This paper deals with the performance evaluation of Softmax and Hierarchical Softmax on large scale classification tasks. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also deals with text classification tasks, which falls under the sub-category cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Additionally, the paper may also be relevant to sub-categories such as cs.CL (Computation and Language) for natural language processing, cs.CV (Computer Vision) for image classification tasks, and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) for general classification tasks.
